data.title: Luminous
data.text:
Brand New Version of Luminous-Lint Coming Soon!

Immense progress is being made on an entirely new mobile-friendly version of Luminous-Lint.

A Beta Release will be available to all individual subscribers later this month to get feedback prior to release.

The old version has now been closed down as we prepare for the next exciting phase of Luminous-Lint.

Many thanks for all your support,
